Class NutiteqOnlineVectorTileLayer

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.nutiteq.layers.Layer
      • com.nutiteq.layers.TileLayer
        • com.nutiteq.layers.VectorTileLayer
          • com.nutiteq.layers.NutiteqOnlineVectorTileLayer

  • public class NutiteqOnlineVectorTileLayer
extends VectorTileLayer
    Specialized online vector tile layer that connects to Nutiteq online tile server.
    This layer is intended as a 'shortcut' to make using Nutiteq online service and vector tiles as simple as possible.
